---
import Container from "../Container.astro";

const cols = [
  {
    title: "서비스",
    links: [
      ["솔루션", "/solutions/"],
      ["AI 가시성 최적화(AVO)", "/ai-visibility-optimization/"],
      ["AI Commerce", "/ai-commerce/"],
      ["가격 안내", "/pricing/"],
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "리소스",
    links: [
      ["AI 검색 용어집", "/glossary/"],
      ["고객사·파트너", "/partners/"],
      ["비전", "/vision/"],
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "회사",
    links: [
      ["회사소개", "/about/"],
      ["문의하기", "/contact/"],
    ],
  },
];
---

<footer class="border-t border-border bg-muted/40 py-16">
  <Container>
    <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.4fr_2fr]">
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <img src="/leadgenlab-wordmark.png" alt="LeadGenLab" width="1024" height="323" class="h-6 w-auto" />
        <p class="text-sm text-fg-muted">AI Visibility Optimization No.1 전문 기업</p>
        <p class="max-w-xs text-xs leading-relaxed text-fg-subtle">
          AI가 추천하는 브랜드가 되도록, AVO Framework로 AI 가시성을 설계·실행·측정합니다.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
        {
          cols.map((col) => (
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-fg">{col.title}</p>
              <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2">
                {col.links.map(([label, href]) => (
                  <li>
                    <a href={href} class="text-sm text-fg-muted transition-colors hover:text-primary">
                      {label}
                    </a>
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 border-t border-border pt-6 text-xs leading-relaxed text-fg-subtle">
      <p>대표 이효석 · 사업자등록번호 109-19-69346</p>
      <p>서울시 성동구 성수일로 99 서울숲AK밸리 8층 · 강남 가로수길 72 · 인천 송도 글로벌 GTM센터</p>
      <p class="mt-2">© {new Date().getFullYear()} LeadGenLab. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</footer>
